Package: DuckDBSpatial
Version: 0.9.0
Date: 2026-03-02
Title: DuckDB-Backed Spatial Data Structures
Description:
    Provides DuckDB-backed implementations of spatial data structures for efficient
    out-of-memory operations on large spatial datasets. The package includes
    optimized spatial operations including st_intersects, st_contains, st_within,
    and more. Ideal for spatial analysis, genomic interval analysis, and other
    spatial workflows requiring memory-efficient operations on large datasets.
